# ── Fetch Method 1: Direct Sweep MCP token (works standalone, no Claude session needed) ──
# Get this from your Sweep dashboard under Settings > MCP / Integrations.
# SWEEP_MCP_TOKEN=your_bearer_token_here

# Optional: override the default Sweep MCP SSE endpoint (default: https://sweepmcp.com/sse)
# SWEEP_MCP_URL=https://sweepmcp.com/sse

# ── Fetch Method 2: Claude session (automatic when running inside Claude Code) ──
# No configuration needed — the CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN is injected automatically
# by the Claude desktop app when you launch the server from within Claude Code.
# If neither token is set, use the /fetch-sfdc slash command in Claude chat.
